data.description: Come check out this beautiful townhome located in The Woods at Elk River. With over 1,400 SQ FT, there is plenty of room for everyone. Enjoy cooking in your new beautiful kitchen with SS appliances and large center island that is perfect for food prep. The home has been freshly painted with new flooring and carpet. The primary bedroom is located on the upper level and boasts a large walk in closet. All of this centrally located near the light rail, parks, schools, big box stores and easy access to HWY 10 & 169. Schedule your showing today! Quick Close Possible.
